Package: heatmapEco
Type: Package
Title: Heatmap Plotter Suited for Economic Data
Version: 0.25
Date: 2016-02-21
Authors@R: person("Tom", "Cui", email = "Tom.Cui@Chicagobooth.edu", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Description: Provides convenience functions for generating heatmaps suitable
   for visualizing economic data. Provides an appealing colour palette, easy entry of policy change lines, outlier visualization and quantile binning of a continuous variable. Built on dplyr, ggplot2 (H. Wickham), zoo (A. Zeileis) and statar (M. Gomez).
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    zoo
Suggests:
    data.table,
    lfe,
    testthat
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
